If you could see how in love we were then.

788
01:20:12,599 --> 01:20:13,884
我怀孕了
I was pregnant.

789
01:20:14,268 --> 01:20:15,508
他没有半点犹豫
He didn't hesitate.

790
01:20:16,145 --> 01:20:17,851
我们当天就结婚了
We were married that same day.

791
01:20:19,690 --> 01:20:21,601
