He was heir to the Roman empire.

792
01:20:22,860 --> 01:20:25,476
他父亲绝不欢迎
And his father could never welcome into the family

793
01:20:25,571 --> 01:20:27,778
婚前怀的小孩进入家族
a child conceived out of wedlock.

794
