But what chance did I have opposite the godfather of Gotham?

796
01:20:38,375 --> 01:20:39,581
在无视我的意愿下…
Against my will...

797
01:20:40,169 --> 01:20:42,581
我们的婚约取消  而我们的孩子…
Our marriage was annulled and our child...

798
01:20:43,255 --> 01:20:44,870
从我的子宫夺走
Ripped from my womb.

799
01:20:47,301 --> 01:20:48,416
他们对我做的事…
What they did to me...

800
01:20:50,012 --> 01:20:51,468
他们所采取的方式…
The way it was done...

801
01:20:53,182 --> 01:20:54,467
让我整个崩溃了
Left me broken.

802
01:20:56,143 --> 01:20:57,474
你曾想复仇
You wanted revenge.

803
01:21:00,731 --> 01:21:01,811
我想要的是伸张正义
I wanted justice.

804
01:21:02,524 --> 01:21:04,105
我来到高谭市  嫁给了
I came to Gotham and married the man

805
01:21:04,193 --> 01:21:06,775
